item.description: library(googleAuthR) library(googleAnalyticsR) library(searchConsoleR) # start with google analytics auth gar_auth("ga.httr-oauth") # can run Google Analytics API calls: ga_account_list() # switch to Seach Console auth gar_auth("sc.httr-oauth") # can now run Search Console API calls: list_websites() .knitr .inline { background-color: #f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #B0B0B0; } .error { font-weight: bold; color: #FF0000; } .warning { font-weight: bold; } .message { font-style: italic; } .source, .output, .warning, .error, .message { padding: 0 1em; border:solid 1px #F7F7F7; } .
